headline: Winners in Second Annual Stevie速 Awards for Technology Excellence Announced
summary: Winners in the 2025 (second annual) Stevie速 Awards for Technology Excellence were announced today. The awards celebrate the remarkable accomplishments of individuals, teams, and organizations shaping the future of technology across all industry sectors. Individuals and organizations worldwide are eligible to enter - public and private, for-profit and non-profit, large and small.
